Standard Libraries: contextlib, sys, wave, os, time, datetime, threading, json, shutil, subprocess, tempfile
webrtcvad: WebRTC Voice Activity Detector
pyaudio: A wrapper for PortAudio
requests: HTTP library
openai: OpenAI's Python client library
deepl: Unofficial Python wrapper for DeepL
dotenv: Python-dotenv
customtkinter: Customized tkinter widgets
tkinter, ttk: Part of the Python Standard Library
sounddevice: An interface to the PortAudio library
gtts: Google Text-to-Speech
pydub: A simple and easy-to-use library to work with audio


